<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="407" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="14.[115,1324,1172,1787]" pageId="14" pageNumber="407">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[121,468,1675,1708]" pageId="14" pageNumber="407">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Jalisco Shrew was only recently described and seems to be threatened by deforestation.
</paragraph>
